One more on it.

00:52:25.470 --> 00:52:28.750
In Greenville, because
of the Electrolux factory

00:52:28.750 --> 00:52:31.910
there were all these suppliers in the area

00:52:31.910 --> 00:52:33.110
to supply the factory,

